import { useState } from "react";

const Login = () => {
    const [viewPdw, setViewPdw] = useState('password')
    return(
        <article className="content-frm-login col-10 col-sm-10 col-lg-6 col-xl-6 m-auto bg-dark">
            <form id='frm-login'>
                <input type='text' name='user' placeholder='Nombre de usuario'/>
                <article className="col-12">
                    <input type={viewPdw} name='pdw' placeholder='Contraseña'/>
                    <button type='button' className='btn-switch-pdw'>
                        <svg width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="bi bi-eye-slash" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M13.359 11.238C15.06 9.72 16 8 16 8s-3-5.5-8-5.5a7.028 7.028 0 0 0-2.79.588l.77.771A5.944 5.944 0 0 1 8 3.5c2.12 0 3.879 1.168 5.168 2.457A13.134 13.134 0 0 1 14.828 8c-.058.087-.122.183-.195.288-.335.48-.83 1.12-1.465 1.755-.165.165-.337.328-.517.486l.708.709z"/>
                            <path d="M11.297 9.176a3.5 3.5 0 0 0-4.474-4.474l.823.823a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 2.829 2.829l.822.822zm-2.943 1.299l.822.822a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.474-4.474l.823.823a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.829 2.829z"/>
                            <path d="M3.35 5.47c-.18.16-.353.322-.518.487A13.134 13.134 0 0 0 1.172 8l.195.288c.335.48.83 1.12 1.465 1.755C4.121 11.332 5.881 12.5 8 12.5c.716 0 1.39-.133 2.02-.36l.77.772A7.029 7.029 0 0 1 8 13.5C3 13.5 0 8 0 8s.939-1.721 2.641-3.238l.708.709z"/>
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M13.646 14.354l-12-12 .708-.708 12 12-.708.708z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                </article>
                <input className='btn text-dark' type='submit' value='Iniciar sesión'/>
            </form>
        </article>
    )
}

export default Login;
